quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  62,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  62,1,"Allah ki tasbeeh kar rahi hai har woh cheez jo asmano mein hai aur har woh cheez jo zameen mein hai badshah hai, Quddoos hai, zabardast aur hakeem hai"
  62,2,"wohi hai jis ne ummiyonke andar aik rasool khud aُnhi mein se uthaya, jo unhen uss ki ayaat sunataa hai, unn ki zindagi sanwarta hai, aur unn ko kitaab aur hikmat ki taleem deta hai halaank iss se pehlay woh khuli gumraahi mein parre hue thay"
  62,3,aur ( is rasool ki bassat ) unn dosray logon ke liye bhi hai jo abhi unn se nahi miley hain
  62,4,"Allah zabardast aur hakeem hai yeh is ka fazl hai, jisay chahta hai deta hai, aur woh bara fazl frmane wala hai"
  62,5,"jin logon ko Touraat ka haamil banaya gaya tha magar unhon ne is ka baar nah utha ya, unn ki misaal uss gadhay ki si hai jis par kitaaben ldi hui hon iss se bhi ziyada buri misaal hai unn logon ki jinhon ne Allah ki ayaat ko jhutla diya hai aisay zaalmon ko Allah hadaayat nahi diya karta"
  62,6,"inn se kaho,"" ae logo jo yahodi ban gay ho, agar tumhe yeh ghamand hai ke baqi sab logon ko chore kar bas tum hi Allah ke chaheetey ho to mout ki tamanna karo agar tum apne iss zeam mein sachey ho """
  62,7,"lekin yeh hargiz is ki tamanna nah karen ge apne krtoton ki wajah se jo yeh kar chuke hain, aur Allah inn zaalmon ko khoob jaanta hai"
  62,8,"inn se kaho,"" jis mout se tum bhagtay ho woh to tumhe aa kar rahay gi phir tum is ke samnay paish kiye jao ge jo posheeda o zahir ka jan-nay wala hai, aur woh tumhe bta day ga ke tum kya kuch karte rahay ho"
  62,9,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab puraka jaye namaz ke liye jummay ke din to Allah ke zikar ki taraf dorro aur khareed o farokht chore do, yeh tumahray liye ziyada behtar hai agar tum jano"
  62,10,"phir jab namaz poori ho jaye to zameen mein phail jao aur Allah ka fazl talaash karo aur Allah ko kasrat se yaad karte raho, shayad ke tumhe Falah naseeb ho jaye"
  62,11,"aur jab unhon ne tijarat aur khail tamasha hotay dekha to is ki taraf lapak gay aur tumhe khara chore diya un se kaho, jo kuch Allah ke paas hai woh khail tamashay aur tijarat se behtar hai aur Allah sab se behtar rizaq dainay wala hai"
